<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to CourierX</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    /* Base Styles */
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    a {
        color: #1E90FF;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        color: white;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    p {
        margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }

    /* Layout */
    .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border-radius: 5px;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: white;
    }

    .email-header {
        background-color: #1E1E1E;
        padding: 25px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
    }

    .email-body {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }

    .email-footer {
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #1E1E1E;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* Components */
    .info-card {
        background-color: white;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .credentials {
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .credentials p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .password {
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 14px;
        background-color: #e5e7eb;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #FFA500;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background-color: #e69500;
    }

    .note {
        background-color: #fff8e1;
        border-left: 4px solid #FFD700;
        padding: 12px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .social-links {
        margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .social-links a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 8px;
        color: #1E90FF;
        font-weight: normal;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to CourierX</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <%= fullname %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for creating an account with CourierX. We're excited to have you on board!</p>

      <div class="info-card">
        <h2>Your Account Information</h2>
        <div class="credentials">
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
          <p><strong>Password:</strong></p>
          <div class="password"><%= password %></div>
        </div>
        <p>For security reasons, we recommend changing your password after first login.</p>
      </div>

      <a href="http://localhost:5175/login" class="btn">Login to Your Account</a>

      <div class="note">
        <h2>Important Security Note</h2>
        <p><strong>Please keep your password confidential.</strong> CourierX will never ask for your password via email or phone.</p>
        <p>If you did not register for a CourierX account, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately.</p>
      </div>

      <p>Need help getting started? Check out our <a href="https://www.courierx.com/guides">Getting Started Guide</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>Â© 2025 CourierX. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://www.courierx.com/privacy" style="color: #fff;">Privacy Policy</a> | 
        <a href="https://www.courierx.com/terms" style="color: #fff;">Terms of Service</a>
      </p>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://facebook.com/courierx">Facebook</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/courierx">Twitter</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/company/courierx">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
      <p>
        Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@courierx.com" style="color: #fff;">support@courierx.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
